      "rationale": "Validation geometry is the FDA generic centrifugal pump, identical to the COU device geometry. Operating conditions span the full COU envelope. Blood analog fluid properties characterized and documented; departure from whole blood viscosity is the primary source of the flagged ±18% uncertainty bound and is explicitly captured in the UQ record. Achieved level equals required level."
