      "rationale": "RANS k-omega SST turbulence model selected based on published benchmark performance for rotating confined flows. Power-law hemolysis model (Giersiepen-Wurzinger) selected with published coefficients. Model form uncertainty assessed via comparison with SST-SAS variant; difference < 6% on hemolysis QoI, included in UQ budget. Achieved level equals required level."
