      "rationale": "Bench hemolysis measurements conducted on n=6 replicate pump units per operating point (30 total measurements). Experimental uncertainty quantified per ASTM F1841. Inter-unit variability characterized and included in validation comparison uncertainty budget. Sample size provides 90% power to detect 15% hemolysis deviation. Achieved level 3 exceeds required level 2."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Equivalency of input parameters",
